{
  "stem": "26142.18",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're giving away-- and he, he would answer to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you don't know how to shovel coal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't know how to hunger, as though you have to learn how to hunger.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's a trait.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you learn it, you know how to, how to be hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's-- you don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He would, he would give away his, his-- take a couple puffs, turn it off, cover himself up, up with over the head with his blanket and go to, go to sleep for another four hours till he would be awake again, when, when in the evening, he would get a little, a little soup or something, whatever they would get, or a little [? margarine. ?] Anyway, but he, he was very smart.",
      "word_count": 74
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He saved my-- I think he saved my, my life two days before liberation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This wasn't heard of-- two days before liberation, I also had an operation in, in, in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the Dachau-- I'll get back to this-- in the Dachau, I, I developed a boil in the back laying, not, laying in, in, in, in skin and bone when they took me in.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in Dachau, when they took me in to the hospital to the [INAUDIBLE], it was, it was a real hospital.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a show place, because Dachau was one of the first concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Germans started it in 1934, '35.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wanted to show the world that this is, this is a modern hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, it was a show place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it really was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came into this hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had anesthesia over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They put you to sleep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, where was I?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were having your operation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had, I had the operation in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
